export default {
    'project.alerts.elevator.coming':'The elevator is coming.',
    'project.alerts.elevator.notExists':'The elevator does not exists.',
    'project.alerts.end':'Thanks for using our services!',
    'project.alerts.password.incorrect.header':'The code you have introduced is incorrect.',
    'project.alerts.password.incorrect.body':'Please introduce the right password of the elevator.',
    'project.alerts.password.noP.header':'The code you have introduced is incorrect.',
    'project.alerts.password.incorrect.body':'Please introduce the right password of the elevator.',

    'project.buttons.coming':'Press when you are at the elevator',
    'project.buttons.submit':'submit',
    'project.text.password':'Password',
    'project.placeholder.password':"Put the password here!"
    
}
